Title: Requires the department of financial services and the division of housing and community renewal to issue an annual report on the housing insurance market for multifamily and nonprofit housing providers
Summary: Requires the department of financial services and the division of housing and community renewal to issue an annual report on the housing insurance market for multifamily and nonprofit housing providers.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the insurance law, in relation to requiring an annual report on the housing insurance market for multifamily and nonprofit housing providers
